    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not like a retreat. there's nothing left to reconnect to. the actual substance, the part that made life worth living... it's just gone. i'm just a hollow vessel going through the routine because i have to. it feels more like i'm just an empty house that someone forgot to tear down.",
