      "content": "Your grief is so heavy right now that the desire to heal feels like a cruel irony, but please know that lights can still be kindled in rooms without floors, even if it feels impossible right now. You don't have to decide forever if light is worth seeking; sometimes, taking even a single, small step toward support can shift something from within. I am here to listen without judgment if you simply wish to sit with me in the dark for a moment.",
